Joe HOCHDERFER v. UNITED STATES. No. 449. Circuit Court of Appeals, Tenth Circuit. March 19, 1931. Ayres, Cowan, McCorkle & Fair, and Clement F. Clark, all of Wichita, Kan., for appellant'. Dan B. Cowie, Asst. U. S. Atty., of Topeka, Kan.

Before LEWIS and McDERMOTT, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Appeal dismissed March 19, 1931, per stipulation, at costs of appellant.
